'''Radu Petre Guran''' (born March 5, 1972) is a [[Romania]]n historian, member of the [[World Academy of Art and Science]]. In 2003, he got a Ph.D from the [[School for Advanced Studies in the Social Sciences]]. He has been the first director of the [[Romanian Cultural Institute]] "Mihai Eminescu" in [[Chişinău]] since September 2010.<ref>[http://www.icr.ro/chisinau/despre-noi-12/echipa-3/petre-guran-director.html Petre Guran, director]</ref><ref>[[Timpul de dimineață]], [http://www.timpul.md/articol/omul-saptamanii-petre-guran-directorul-institutului-cultural-roman-m--eminescu-din-chisinau-28989.html Omul Săptămânii: Petre Guran, directorul Institutului Cultural Român „M. Eminescu” din Chişinău] </ref>
